translated: Åberg, Sven Folke, senior mechanical engineer, Norrköping, b. 10/7/91 in Mjölby to inspector August Fredr. Å. and Emma Carolina Pettersson. Married in 19 with Sigrid Erlandson. Children: Sven Fredrik b. 20, Tor b. 22, Britt b. 23. — High school graduate in Lund 10, temporary student at KTH 11-12, regular student 12-14, graduated (M) 14. Trainee at SJ 14, assistant engineer at the machinery department in Gothenburg 17-24, at the machinery department in Kiruna 24-29, machinery engineer at Kar Iskr.-Växjö ironworks from 30-34 and at Växjö railway from 35-40, at S.J. since 41, senior machinery engineer in Växjö from 43-46, and in Norrköping since 46.
